a, b, c
T (>0)
T=T_0 (1+ax+by)e^{cz}
\nabla T = \left({\partial T\over\partial x},{\partial T\over\partial y},{\partial T\over\partial z}\right)
T
{\partial T\over \partial x}
T_0
e^{cz}
{\partial T\over \partial x} = {\partial \over \partial x}\left[(T_0e^{cz})(1+ax+by)\right] = (T_0e^{cz}){\partial\over \partial x}(1+ax+by) = (T_0e^{cz})(a) = aT_0e^{cz}\,.
{\partial T\over\partial y}
{\partial T\over\partial z}
{\partial \over \partial z}\left[T_0(1+ax+by)e^{cz}\right]  = T_0(1+ax+by){\partial\over \partial z}(e^{cz}) = T_0(1+ax+by)(ce^{cz}) = cT_0(1+ax+by)e^{cz}\,.
